    <description>Migrated from the Lead changes process using multiple criteria.
New Version (v3) includes condition that prevents changing the owner for leads that their owner was previously changed, causing the status to change which then triggers an additional owner change.
New Version (v5) includes runtime improvement using assign vs update records + new task 16955- if lead is part of approves mailing campaign, the lead will be updated to lost with the lost reason: קמפיין הצטרפות לדיוור שיווקי

AM: 25032025- 1885669268- refactor</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>fISNEW</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>ISNEW()</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>fNOW</name>
        <dataType>DateTime</dataType>
        <expression>NOW()</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>fOwnerIsUserAndNotConverted</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>AND(NOT(BEGINS(PRIORVALUE({!$Record.OwnerId} ) , &apos;005&apos;))
                ,BEGINS({!$Record.OwnerId}, &apos;005&apos;),
                 {!$Record.IsConverted}
         )</expression>
    </formulas>
